<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idee3d6439-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s518f"><num value="518f">§ 518f.</num><heading> Limitation on total expenditures</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The total amount expended by the Secretary from the Tobacco Trust Fund to make payments under sections 518a and 518b of this title and for the other authorized purposes of the Fund shall not exceed $10,140,000,000.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idee3d643a-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/pl/108/357/tVI/s627">Pub. L. 108–357, title VI, § 627</ref>, <date date="2004-10-22">Oct. 22, 2004</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/118/1534">118 Stat. 1534</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="idee3d643b-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="idee3d643c-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDate" id="idee3d643d-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section applicable to the 2005 and subsequent crops of tobacco, see <ref href="/us/pl/108/357/s643">section 643 of Pub. L. 108–357</ref>, set out as a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t7/s518">section 518 of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
</notes>
